snippet.title: SAMAA TV
snippet.description:
SAMAA TV is a 24-hour national television channel in Pakistan. 

IMPORTANT NOTICE: SAMAA TV does indeed have a policy to retract copyright infringements for YouTube creators. 
We will take each case under consideration on merit. 
Please email copyrights@samaa.tv  
June 11, 2020: Please note we do NOT levy any charges to retract a copyright strike. If any member of staff claims any financial recompense, please report it to us immediately. Our staff does not handle YouTube financial transactions on a one-to-one basis. 
If you have any queries please email Editor Digital Properties mahim.maher@samaa.tv  

If you believe your copyrighted work is appearing on SAMAA TV without permission, please notify us at copyrights@samaa.tv
If you wish to reach a member of staff please find the list here: https://www.samaa.tv/contact-us/

If you wish to reach a member of the website, please write to website@samaa.tv 
www.samaa.tv
